  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "As the border was open because the Russian Army went into Poland, the border was open, thousands of Jewish people from the town, from the places Hitler had occupied, left and they went to Russia.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Of course, the border was open.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Without any questions, Russia let them go in.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Wait a minute.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "People went in.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Then the Red Army already not far from Chelm.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "One day, a-- a-- a Russian tank-- a Russian tank fast went through [?",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Chelm ?] Street, the main street.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "A tank, a small tank compared with the tanks that we [INAUDIBLE], small just a little small sports car.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But it's fast.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "These-- these people [INAUDIBLE] they knew already that's the spying, they're spying what Chelm look like.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "They was like, that's [INAUDIBLE] spying.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "A few days later, the Red Army in Chelm-- Red Army in Chelm.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Compare the atrocities what the German done to the Yiddish people in the places [INAUDIBLE] and compare with the Russian Army that was coming in, was a heaven.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "The only thing both happened, the anti-Semite-- the Polish anti-Semite from Chelm, they hiding because they're frightened.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "They're hiding like they can't see it.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And then after that, after a few days, was a agreement with [INAUDIBLE] and [INAUDIBLE], the two foreign ministers, [INAUDIBLE], the German foreign minister, both of the Russian foreign minister where the new border will be.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And I listen-- I sit back at work and I listen to the radio are I hear [INAUDIBLE] mention where the new border will be.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "They mentioned every village, every-- every little town, every town where the new border will be.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "[?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "As ?] [? we ?] [? looked ?] [? it ?] Chelm will be under the German.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "Oh.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "Not good.",
      "word_count": 2
    }
  ],
